---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "June 10, 2026";
const email = "admin@ar27111994.dev";
const siteUrl = "https://ar27111994.dev";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Ahmed Rehan"
  description="Privacy policy for AI agents, tools, and skills published by Ahmed Rehan."
>
  <main class="privacy-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← ar27111994.dev</a>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </header>

      <section class="section">
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy describes how Ahmed Rehan ("<strong>I</strong>", "<strong>me</strong>", or "<strong>my</strong>")
          collects, uses, and handles information in connection with AI agents, skills, tools, and software
          products published on third-party marketplaces (including but not limited to Capafy) and available
          at <a href={siteUrl}>{siteUrl}</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>1. Information I Collect</h2>
        <p>
          My downloadable AI agents and skill packages (<strong>Download mode products</strong>) run entirely
          on your local machine or within your own AI agent environment. They do not transmit data to my
          servers. No personal information, usage data, or conversation history is collected by me when you
          use these products.
        </p>
        <p>
          When you contact me directly (e.g. via support email), I receive only the information you choose to send.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>2. How I Use Information</h2>
        <p>
          Any information you voluntarily provide through direct contact (email, GitHub issues, marketplace
          messaging) is used solely to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your support requests or questions</li>
          <li>Improve product quality and documentation</li>
        </ul>
        <p>I do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>3. Third-Party Platforms</h2>
        <p>
          My products are distributed through third-party marketplaces (e.g. Capafy). When you purchase or
          download a product through these platforms, their own privacy policies apply to any data they collect
          during the transaction. I am not responsible for the privacy practices of third-party platforms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>4. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          This portfolio website (<a href={siteUrl}>{siteUrl}</a>) does not use tracking cookies or
          third-party analytics services. No cookies are set on your device when you visit this site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          I retain support correspondence only as long as necessary to resolve your request. You may
          request deletion of any personal information you have provided by emailing me.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          My products and services are not directed at children under the age of 13. I do not knowingly
          collect personal information from children.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this
          page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of my products after changes are posted
          constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact me at:
          <a href={`mailto:${email}`}>{email}</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg, #0a0a0a);
    color: var(--color-text, #e5e5e5);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent, #7c6af7);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-heading, #fff);
  }

  .meta {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-muted, #888);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-heading, #fff);
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text, #ccc);
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  li {
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text, #ccc);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent, #7c6af7);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
